{"tid":1524342,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我有一個建議：請你地勇武唔好再上水！","createTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:59:43.000Z","uid":184597,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"33ab9bd4090456cadb9e3ee24487a36bbcaeaace","tid":1524342,"uid":184597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"我愛你地每一位真&middot;香港人<br />\n<br />\n如果睇左標題，想負皮、屌我，冇問題<br />\n但我懇請您地睇埋我以下所講<br />\n（可能有啲隱晦，但請你思考一下我本意）<br />\n<br />\n》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要做一名忍者</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一</span></span><br />\n一個忍者，非執行任務既時候，佢地係平民，係和理非，越低調越好。<br />\n如果遇上挑釁，要以和理非既手法處理。最終可能會被查，被拉，但你本身乜都冇做過，就算屈你，罪名都唔會重得去邊。<br />\n切記，你係一個平民，你係一個和理非，一切既忍耐，係為左保留有用之身。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">二</span></span><br />\n當忍者執行任務時，係完全另一種作風。<br />\n佢地會選擇突襲，無聲無息，非常迅速，非常猛烈。完事，即走。事敗，即走。<br />\n敵方唔知佢地幾時出現，邊度出現，無法佈防，因此佢地會恐懼。"},{"pid":"2a833e77805899e78d3490f97a40b128372917f5","tid":1524342,"uid":184597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"自推！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我覺得係時候改變模式喇！</span></span>"},{"pid":"8cd072fa701a940f4b703d519da63e3414521c95","tid":1524342,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:19:52.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=a8437f33\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=c1432a9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70hZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3643c75a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"60431b3743a60cb22c5f14401bd763995ce6b8e6","tid":1524342,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0a2c78ffa76aebb3612be49a1ac4b5d2134118d5","tid":1524342,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7e6bec1dde2a19efae4fc3a3c8933536e54d09f","tid":1524342,"uid":269697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n宜家啲人好猾惑<br />\n螳螂捕蟬黃雀在後<br />\n一定要夠<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">醒目</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31ac6378949fad558b5c2e4814f36d019325895","tid":1524342,"uid":287112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d01f711c58a0da39228554540341c97548c9b81","tid":1524342,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:53.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"fe05bbcfa88e93605ed1aaf5129618bdcd60e4cb","tid":1524342,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:26:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3949128e94b8dbefee4f0c95e78a71e76975675d","tid":1524342,"uid":227981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a833e77805899e78d3490f97a40b128372917f5","tid":1524342,"uid":184597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201